addAddressSetting(string,address,address.details: Advocate of _creatorTAOId adds an address setting

params._associatedTAOId: The taoId that the setting affects
params._creatorTAOId: The taoId that created the setting
params._extraData: Catch-all string value to be stored if exist
params._settingName: The human-readable name of the setting
params._value: The address value of the setting

addBoolSetting(string,bool,address,addre.details: Advocate of _creatorTAOId adds a bool setting

params._associatedTAOId: The taoId that the setting affects
params._creatorTAOId: The taoId that created the setting
params._extraData: Catch-all string value to be stored if exist
params._settingName: The human-readable name of the setting
params._value: The bool value of the setting

addBytesSetting(string,bytes32,address,a.details: Advocate of _creatorTAOId adds a bytes32 setting

params._associatedTAOId: The taoId that the setting affects
params._creatorTAOId: The taoId that created the setting
params._extraData: Catch-all string value to be stored if exist
params._settingName: The human-readable name of the setting
params._value: The bytes32 value of the setting

addStringSetting(string,string,address,a.details: Advocate of _creatorTAOId adds a string setting

params._associatedTAOId: The taoId that the setting affects
params._creatorTAOId: The taoId that created the setting
params._extraData: Catch-all string value to be stored if exist
params._settingName: The human-readable name of the setting
params._value: The string value of the setting

addUintSetting(string,uint256,address,ad.details: Advocate of _creatorTAOId adds a uint setting

params._associatedTAOId: The taoId that the setting affects
params._creatorTAOId: The taoId that created the setting
params._extraData: Catch-all string value to be stored if exist
params._settingName: The human-readable name of the setting
params._value: The uint256 value of the setting

approveSettingCreation(uint256,bool).details: Advocate of Setting's _associatedTAOId approves setting creation

params._settingId: The ID of the setting to approve

finalizeSettingCreation(uint256).details: Advocate of Setting's _creatorTAOId finalizes the setting creation once the setting is approved

params._settingId: The ID of the setting to be finalized

getSettingIdByTAOName(address,string).details: Get setting Id given an associatedTAOId and settingName

getSettingTypes().return: The setting type value for addressThe setting type value for boolThe setting type value for bytesThe setting type value for stringThe setting type value for uint

getSettingValuesById(uint256).details: Get setting values by setting ID.	Will throw error if the setting is not exist or rejected.
getSettingValuesById(uint256).return: the uint256 value of this setting IDthe bool value of this setting IDthe address value of this setting IDthe bytes32 value of this setting IDthe string value of this setting ID

getSettingValuesByTAOName(address,string.details: Get setting values by taoId and settingName.	Will throw error if the setting is not exist or rejected.
getSettingValuesByTAOName(address,string.return: the uint256 value of this setting IDthe bool value of this setting IDthe address value of this setting IDthe bytes32 value of this setting IDthe string value of this setting ID

setNameAccountRecoveryAddress(address).details: The AO set the NameAccountRecovery Address

setWhitelist(address,bool).details: Whitelist `_account` address to transact on behalf of others

settingNameExist(string,address).details: Check whether or not a setting name of an associatedTAOId exist

params._associatedTAOId: The taoId that the setting affects
params._settingName: The human-readable name of the setting

settingTypeLookup(uint256).details: Get setting type of a setting ID
settingTypeLookup(uint256).return: the setting type value	   setting type 1 => uint256, 2 => bool, 3 => address, 4 => bytes32, 5 => string

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfer ownership of The AO to new address

params._theAO: The new address to be transferred
